    <item>
      <title>习近平在美国大选前发表讲话强调就业问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-01/xi-highlights-employment-woes-in-speech-published-before-us-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国家主席习近平在新发表的讲话中强调了中国就业市场面临的压力，并指出中国这个世界第二大经济体正处于动荡时期，官员们试图阻止经济增长放缓。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-01/xi-highlights-employment-woes-in-speech-published-before-us-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 02:31:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国投票前朝鲜发射“新型”洲际弹道导弹以增加载荷</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-01/north-korea-fired-new-icbm-for-bigger-payloads-before-us-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[朝鲜本周发射的一枚洲际弹道导弹创下了飞行记录，这可能使领导人金正恩能够装载更重的弹头并帮助他对美国本土实施核打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-01/north-korea-fired-new-icbm-for-bigger-payloads-before-us-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 02:30:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>勒布朗·詹姆斯援引特朗普的种族言论支持哈里斯</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/lebron-james-endorses-kamala-harris-for-president-assailing-trump-over-rhetoric</link>
      <description><![CDATA[世界上最受欢迎的运动员之一勒布朗·詹姆斯 (LeBron James) 周四正式支持民主党副总统卡马拉·哈里斯 (Kamala Harris)，并在一段视频中斥责唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump)，该视频强调了共和党候选人在种族问题上经常发表的煽动性言论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/lebron-james-endorses-kamala-harris-for-president-assailing-trump-over-rhetoric</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 22:02:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>博茨瓦纳早期选举结果显示执政党惨败</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/botswana-election-early-tallies-point-to-shock-loss-for-ruling-party</link>
      <description><![CDATA[博茨瓦纳选举的初步结果表明，过去 58 年来统治这个钻石资源丰富的国家的政党将失去对权力的控制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/botswana-election-early-tallies-point-to-shock-loss-for-ruling-party</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 21:17:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>芝加哥学校董事会主席宣誓一周后辞职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/chicago-school-board-president-resigns-a-week-after-taking-oath</link>
      <description><![CDATA[芝加哥教育委员会主席米切尔·约翰逊 (Mitchell Johnson) 于周四辞职，此前他发布的一些有争议的社交媒体帖子被曝光。在宣誓就职一周后，约翰逊辞职。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/chicago-school-board-president-resigns-a-week-after-taking-oath</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 21:13:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国正在浪费对习近平的隐藏优势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-10-31/navigating-us-china-tensions-is-getting-more-complicated-ahead-of-elections</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国对中国 14 亿人民的软实力影响力正因唐纳德·特朗普八年前散播的恶意和猜疑而迅速削弱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-10-31/navigating-us-china-tensions-is-getting-more-complicated-ahead-of-elections</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 21:00:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯抓住特朗普保护女性的誓言，无论她们“喜欢与否”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/harris-hits-trump-vow-to-protect-women-if-they-like-it-or-not</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯抓住唐纳德·特朗普的言论，即如果当选，他将“保护”女性——无论她们“喜欢与否”——来攻击其共和党对手在生殖权利和其他自由方面的立场，以吸引郊区和独立女性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/harris-hits-trump-vow-to-protect-women-if-they-like-it-or-not</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 15:38:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>太平洋岛国领导人称中国推动台湾问题转向</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/pacific-island-leader-says-china-is-pressing-for-taiwan-switch</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾在太平洋地区的最后一个外交盟友之一的领导人表示，台湾正面临来自中国越来越大的压力，要求其终止对台北的支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/pacific-island-leader-says-china-is-pressing-for-taiwan-switch</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 03:27:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本执政党在选举受挫后将何去何从</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/japan-election-how-is-a-coalition-formed-why-the-ldp-lost</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自 1955 年成立以来，自民党执政日本已有四年，但在 10 月 27 日的选举中失去了多数席位，在全球焦虑加剧之际造成了政治不确定性。新政府必须在 11 月底前组建，自民党和主要反对党都寻求获得小党派的足够支持，以管理世界第四大经济体。自民党的政策重点包括加税以支付增加的军费开支]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/japan-election-how-is-a-coalition-formed-why-the-ldp-lost</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 04:33:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
